title: See who took home an Emmy Award
text:
(CNN) The winners for the 71st Primetime Emmy Awards are being announced Sunday.

Heading into the night, all eyes are" Game of Thrones ," which had a record 32 nominations, the most earned in a single year by any drama series. At the Creative Arts Emmys, held last weekend, the show picked up 10 wins.

But can the series, which ended this year, continue its momentum?

Follow along below with our ongoing list of winners in major categories, which will be updated as they are announced.

Outstanding supporting actor in a comedy series
